text:
Divya Rao Feb . 13 . 2017 Saif Ali Khan, Taimur Ali Khan, Kareena Kapoor 
Kareena Kapoor and Saif Ali Khan brought into this world their little bundle of joy – Taimur Ali Khan – two months ago. The Internet lost its shit and went crazy over the name… but Bebo and Saif couldn’t be bothered. Kareena was attending events looking like an absolute boss . Check out pictures here . She also spoke about the controversy surrounding his name, addressing that this is their personal matter only, and rightly so. 
We landed our hands on the first photos of this little Prince, and boy, is he breathtakingly gorgeous! Reportedly, this picture was Saif whatsapp picture and has been picked up from there. Look at that golden hair and those eyes… he looks just like his mommy, doesn’t he? A photo posted by Kareena Kapoor Khan FC (@kareenakapoorteam) on Feb 12, 2017 at 8:06am PST A photo posted by Kareena Kapoor Arab Fan Club ❁ (@kareenakapoor.arabiic) on Feb 12, 2017 at 9:05am PST Do you see the resemblance here? A photo posted by SalmanKhan-KareenaKapoorKhan (@sallubeboteam) on Feb 12, 2017 at 9:32am PST 
He is one gorgeous little baby boy! 19
